author: Joshua Friemel
title: Cowboys fans help explain Tony Romo's advice to Brandon Weeden in Top 25 fan-made memes
text:
Evan if the Brandon Weeden era is over with the Dallas Cowboys, the memes are not getting benched.
Readers had some interesting ideas using our meme generator to get some insight on what Tony Romo was saying to Brandon Weeden.
Below are the top 25 fan-made memes from SportsDay readers.
25. Thanks, Yogi.
24. Glass-half full
23. Weeden's revelation
22. Tim Tebow sighting
21. Escape plan
20. #Throwback
19. Silence!
18. Insert obligatory crowny comment here
17. (Don't) Be yourself
16. Either way...
15. THEN WHY HAVEN'T YOU
14. How-to
13. America's team
12. Follow that yellow brick road...to JerryWorld
11. A deep and terrible rage
10. We-done
9. Like Mike
8. *Brandon runs off stage while a camera follows
7. The ambidextrous quarterback
6. ...then what?
5. Rage quit
4. <Mind blown>
3. Name's Weeden. Brandon Weeden.
2. Proper motivation
1. It's not going to happen
